General Metrics of the Server:
                               Sever's current state (running or not) via ping etc

                               In CPU:
                                      CPU used
                                      CPU load
                                      CPU temperature
                               In Memeroy and disk:
                                      Memory usage
                                      Disk space usage
                                      Ulimits                                     
                               In Input outputs:
                                      I/O
                                      IO read and IO write
                               In Network:
                                      Network traffic
                                      TCP connection states
                                      Bandwidth usage

                                Application metrics:
                                
                               SSL certificate validate status
                               Latency
                               Errors
